    "## 4. Model — ResNet-50\n",
    "\n",
    "- Pré-entraîné ImageNet (transfer learning)\n",
    "- **Pas de dropout** — Gayatri & Aarthy (2024) n'utilisent pas de dropout\n",
    "- Tête de classification : FC → 8 classes\n",
    "- Backbone entraîné entièrement dès l'epoch 1 (pas de warmup)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "model",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-04-30T09:58:23.788323Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-04-30T09:58:23.788045Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-04-30T09:58:25.357380Z"
