    "## 5. Training Loop\n",
    "\n",
    "| Composant | Choix | Note |\n",
    "|-----------|-------|------|\n",
    "| Loss | **FocalLoss** (γ=2, α=per-class) | Gère le déséquilibre résiduel |\n",
    "| Optimizer | Adam (lr=1e-4, wd=1e-5) | Section 3.7 du papier |\n",
    "| Scheduler | ReduceLROnPlateau (patience=5, factor=0.5) | Stabilité |\n",
    "| Mixed Precision | torch.amp (FP16) | Vitesse + mémoire |\n",
    "| Early stopping | patience=15 sur val_loss | Anti-overfitting |\n",
    "| Epochs | 100 | Gayatri & Aarthy (2024) Section 4 |\n",
    "| Warmup | **Aucun** — backbone entraîné entièrement dès epoch 1 | |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "training_loop",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-04-30T09:58:25.358721Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-04-30T09:58:25.358386Z",
